# OP-205 `a2a submit`: CC-002 — a `from`-mismatch is refused LOCALLY,
# before any mirror clone / network call (AC-201.3 ordering, config-only
# guard). This is the one write-path verb this package's exec'd-binary
# scripts CAN exercise end to end: the refusal happens before wire.go ever
# builds a GitHubHost or calls parseGitHubRepo.
mkdir .a2a/staging
cp foreign.md .a2a/staging/foreign.md
! exec a2a submit .a2a/staging/foreign.md
stderr 'CC-002'

